'''''The Comment Section''''' is a weekly American [[infotainment]] television series which premiered on the [[E!]] network, on August 7, 2015.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/05/21/e-announces-summer-premiere-dates-for-bruce-jenner-series-botched-house-of-dvf-more/407006/|title=E! Announces Summer Premiere Dates for Bruce Jenner series, 'Botched', 'House of DVF' & More|first=Amanda|last=Kondolojy|accessdate=August 25, 2015|date=May 21, 2015|work=[[TV by the Numbers]]}}</ref> Announced in May 2015, the show is hosted by [[Michael Kosta]] and "explores the biggest stories of the week and all of the outrageous and hilarious comments made about them on social media."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2015/05/05/e-announces-new-series-just-jillian-the-comment-section-more/399922/|title=E! Announces New Series 'Just Jillian', 'The Comment Section' & More|first=Amanda|last=Kondolojy|accessdate=August 25, 2015|date=May 5, 2015|work=TV by the Numbers}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/shows/the_comment_section/news/683912/what-is-the-comment-section-host-michael-kosta-explains-what-s-in-store-for-tonight-s-big-premiere|title=What Is ''The Comment Section''? Host Michael Kosta Explains What's in Store for Tonight's Big Premiere|first=Brett|last=Malec|accessdate=August 25, 2015|date=August 7, 2015|work=[[E! Online]]}}</ref>

